title: Interceptor Command (1943) Secrets, Spies, and Submarines—The Battle Beneath the Waves!

sources.title: Interceptor Command (1943) Secrets, Spies, and Submarines—The Battle Beneath the Waves!
sources.description:
The FBI launches a hunt for spies transmitting covert messages to enemy submarines.

Submarine Alert is a 1943 American war thriller film directed by Frank McDonald, and written by Maxwell Shane.

Main actors:
Richard Arlen - Lewis J. "Lew" Deerhold
Wendy Barrie - FBI Agent Ann Patterson
Nils Asther - Dr. Arthur Huneker
Roger Pryor - G.B. Fleming
Abner Biberman - Commander Toyo
Marc Lawrence - Vincent Bela
John Miljan - Mr. Bambridge / Capt. Haigas
Patsy Nash - Tina Deerhold
Ralph Sanford - FBI Agent Freddie Grayson

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/nJO5Ns07Cpk
